bharata ki jidipi pe kucha kahana chahata hu.n , padhiyega| kamgresa sarakara ke vaqta vittiya varsha 2013-2014 mem bharata ki jidipi 4.7 thi , jisaka havala dete hue usa vaqta ke ghoshita pradhanamamtri shri modi ji ne manamohana sarakara pe ka.di tippani karate hue janata se apane haqa mem vota ma.nga tha , aura bharata ki arthavyavastha ko behatara karane ka vada kiya tha , jise sacha manate hue janata ne unhem vota diya aura bharata ke ujjavala bhavishya ke lie unhem pradhanamamtri banaya| pradhanamamtri banane ke bada janavari 2015 mem modi sarakara mem bharata ki jidipi ke ganana ka svarupa hi badala dala aura jo jidipi manamohana sarakara ke vaqta 4.7 thi vahi jidipi ganana ka svarupa badala die jane ke karana modi sarakara ke vaqta 6.9 ho gai| usa vaqta ke rbi gavarnara raghurama rajana ne isape ka.di tippani karate hue kaha tha : - `` mana lijie ki eka bachche ki mam apane bachche ki dekhabhala ke lie dusare bachche ki mam ko 500 rupaye deti hai . dusare bachche ki mam bhi pahale bachche ki mam ko apane bachche ki dekhabhala ke lie 500 rupaye deti hai| jidipi ki ganana mem isase 1000 rupaye ju.da jayemge . lekina , kya sachamucha isase arthavyavastha behatara hui , kyomki donom ka bhugatana to apasa mem kata kara shunya ho gaya ! '' maujuda vaqta mem notabamdi ke bavajuda modi sarakara ne bharata ki jidipi 7.0 batai hai , agara manamohana sarakara ke vaqta ke jidipi ganana ke svarupa se dekha jae to ye jidipi 4.7 ke asa pasa hi hai| yaha.n bhi modi sarakara ne hama janata ko phira se bhari dhokha diya hai , bharata mem bajata satra hamesha marcha mem shuru hua hai , vajaha hai vittiya varsha ka 1 apraila se shuru hona , jaha.n faravari ke akira mem maujuda vittiya varsha ki akari riporta ati hai , jisake amka.dom ko dhyana mem rakha kara ane vale vittiya varsha ke lie bajata banaya jata hai| dhyana dene vali bata ye hai ki , modi sarakara ne sala 2017-2018 ka bajata sala 2016-2017 ke tisari timahi ke adhara para hi bana liya , jisame notabamdi se hue nuksana ka koi zikra nahim hai , kyomki notabamdi ke bada vali akari timahi ka deta 28 faravari 2017 ko aya hai| aba apa ye somchiye apa bevaqufa kaba bane ? jaba apane modi ko vota diya taba , ya aba , jaba modi sarakara amka.do ka svarupa badala kara hamem bevaqufa bana rahi hai| hama to aja bhi 69 % logom mem hi shumara haim jinhomne bevaqufa banane se imkara kara diya tha , para apa 31 % logom ki bevaqufi ka nuksana pure bharata ko jhelana pa.da raha hai , apane chetra ke bijepi vidhayakom-samsadom se puchie unhomne aisa kyom kiya , chupa mata rahiye||

bura laga hai| apa ne kaha ki apa `` iit ke imjiniyara '' hai , to evm ko haika karane ke 10 tarike bata sakate hai | maim bhi iit ka imjiniyara ( electrical ) hu.n aura maim apako isa samsthana ki ijjata mitati mem nahim milane dumga| aja apako kucha tathyom se samana karavata hu.n| apane aja se kariba 25 sala pahale iit kha.dagapura se mekenikala imjiniyarimga kiya| apa janata ko bevakupha bana sakate hai para eka imjiniyara ko nahim| eka mekenikala imjiniyara hone ke nate apa evm ke bare mem kucha nahim janate| evm ke bare mem j~nana hone ke lie apako ic design , material science , communication system , electronics , embedded system , microprocessors and programming ka knowledge hona jaruri hai | imjiniyara to samanyataya 2 sala mem saba bhula jate hai agara unaka nata imjiniyarimga se tuta gaya ho aura apa ko to 25 sala bita chuke hai , isalie `` iit ka imjiniyara '' hone ke nama para logom ko bevakupha banana bamda kijiye| apa janate bhi hai evm kaise kama karata hai ? evm eka stand-alone mashina hai , isaka bahara ki duniya se koi nata nahim , ise software ke madhyama se haika karana to lagabhaga namumakina hai| ha.n agara koi jake chipa badala aye to sambhava hai , isako rokane ke lie bhi chunava ayoga avashyaka prashasanika kadama uthata hai| apa eka hare huve rajaneta ke rupa maim evm para prashna uthayem para eka `` iit ka imjiniyara '' hone ke nate nahim| vaise eka satya ye bhi hai ki koi iit ka ho jane matra se achcha imjiniyara nahim ho jata| achche imjiniyara to vo hai jinhomne evm jaisi mashina banayim , aura isaka eka eka hissa purna rupa se bharatiya banaya taki kisi videshi ko bhi na pata chala pae ki evm kaise kama karati hai | eka himdi nyuza chainala ke jane mane patrakara rajata sharma ne apako iit ka manufacturing defect karara diya | kucha to sharma karo , iits ki kitani bejjati karavaoge| khaira phira bhi apa ko lagata hai ki evm haika ho sakati hai to ye gadhe ki taraha dhemchu dhemchu karana bamda karo | chunava ka ek aur nam bhi hai `` din e qayyim '' iska arth hai jo hamesha rahe|||||||| dharmo ke nam se hi yeh bat sabit ho gayi ki jab vohi dharam ishvar ne bharat me bheja to uska nam sanatan pada kyuki
